Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=16}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are you\Nslamming into walls?! - OG}Why are you slamming into the walls?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:06.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's going on?\NSo he can't go on after all?! - OG}What's wrong? Did you\Nfinally reach your limit?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not it! He can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His eyesight has weakened\Nbecause his retinas got hurt! - OG}With his retinas damaged,\Nhis eyesight is weakening!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?! You can't see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It started running like crazy! - OG}It set off in a crazy dash!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Keep them encircled!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:32.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stop the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NFire the trench mortars already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stop, Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're in no shape to keep running anymore! - OG}You're in no shape to keep going!{Z/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He says that he promised Sodom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:54.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He told Sodom, "Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:59.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll carry everyone for you!" - OG}I'll carry everyone for the both of us!"{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,G-Gomorrah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:08.04,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,They were inside its stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:11.84,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,I can't eat anymore. I'm full.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.88,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's take them back with us for emergency food. - OG}{Take 'em with us as emergency food. - Z}Take 'em back home as emergency food.{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.43,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Bro! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.10,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Some pirates beat up Sodom and Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:25.56,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve\Nmessing with my underlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:36.57,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! You're injured! Don't dance!\NSodom! Gomorrah! - OG}Hey, you're injured!\NDon't dance, Sodom and Gomorrah!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:46.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's a dead end ahead!\NHe'll crash into it and die! - OG}There's a dead end ahead!\NHe'll die if he crashes into it!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gomorrah! Stop! Don't run blindly! - OG}Gomorroah! Stop! Don't rush around blindly!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:50.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dead end? - OG}A dead end?{Evo: I don't think the OG is necessarily wrong, it just didn't quite sit right with me to not have the article}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do you see one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's the courthouse, Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:46.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,W-We made it! Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This report is for all units! - OG}{Attention all units! - Z}Reporting to all units!{arch: Doesn't sound like he has a lot of authority, so I'm making clear it's a report and not a command.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:53.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The king bull the pirates were riding on broke\Nthrough the encirclement in Block D! - OG}The pirates' king bull broke through\Nthe encirclement in Block D!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They've just reached the courthouse plaza! - OG}They've reached the courthouse plaza!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat! The pirates...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:04.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Look at this, Funkfreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:08.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's a golden transponder snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:14.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This glittering transponder snail\Nis indeed a valuable item. - OG}As it gives you the authority\Nto exercise a buster call,{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:20.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Only those with permission\Nfrom at least a Marine admiral can have one, as it gives the authority to exercise a buster call. - OG}{\q2}you can't carry this glittering transponder snail\Nwithout authority from at least a Marine admiral.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:26.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,In order for me to exercise a buster call,\NAokiji temporarily entrusted it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:34.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Once the revival of the weapon becomes reality,\NI'll be able to carry this myself, - OG}{With the weapon's revival close at hand,\NI'll be able to carry this myself, - Z}{Once I make the revival of the weapon\Ninto reality, I'll hold this power at all times, - Evo}{\q2}Once the revival of the weapon becomes reality,\NI'll hold this power at all times,{Z - changed the idiom a bit: "make something a reality" or "turn something into a reality" so I chose the latter construction}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:40.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{instead of having some admiral entrust it to me, and control troops at will. - OG}and I'll no longer have to obtain an admiral's\Nspecial permission just to control troops.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:49.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just by pressing this button,\Nan entire island can be wiped out. - OG}With the push of this one button,\Nan entire island will be wiped out.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:54.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Authority can be like a weapon too, huh? - OG}Authority is like a weapon too, huh?{rangicus}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chief Spandam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Knock on the door first! - OG}Knock first!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I almost accidentally pressed the button! - OG}I almost pressed the button!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry. But I was told\Nthat this is an emergency. - OG}I-I'm sorry, but I was told\Nthat this is an emergency.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's a call from Enies Lobby's main island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:17.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A call?! They should've\Ncalled this room directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Th– {\i1}Hey{\i0}! The receiver is off the hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Who keeps doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You just said that there's\Nan emergency or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Spanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:52.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's apparently an emergency report\Nfrom Enies Lobby's main island. - OG}Apparently there's an emergency report\Nfrom Enies Lobby's main island.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:57.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's probably not a real emergency, but you\Ncan probably guess what it's about, right? - OG}It's probably not a real emergency,\Nbut you can guess what it's about, right?{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What happened to Straw Hat Luffy, -OG}{And he struggled so valiantly\Nagainst five of our soldiers! - Z}After he fought so hard\Nto beat five of my guards,{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{who worked hard to beat up a whole five soldiers... - OG}{Poor little Straw Hat Luffy... - Z}{poor little Straw Hat Luffy got\Nstomped into the ground - Evo}just picture poor little Straw Hat Luffy\Nbeing stomped into the ground{arch: it raises CPS but something like this is definitely necessary. OG is very literal, but the expressions just don't work in English - he's asking rhethorical questions like "gee, I wonder what became of them...", basically forcing Robin to think about them. I tried this line to convey his cruelty a bit more.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:13.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How your friends got stomped by\N the strongest gatekeepers, Oimo and Kashi... - OG}{And our strongest gatekeepers, Oimo and\NKashi, stomped your friends into the ground. - Z}by our strongest gatekeepers, Oimo and Kashi,\Nalong with the rest of your friends.{Evo: I think I got the timing right on this from looking at the frames, but please correct me if I'm wrong. Need to take some time to properly look at a tutorial for timing tips cuz I struggled with this one change.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:21.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's listen together and hear what happened\Nto the idiots who rebelled against the World Government! - OG}{\q2}Let's listen together and hear what became of the idiots\Nwho rebelled against the World Government!{arch: lit. it's more like "hear how they amounteed to nothing"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You're a real scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is Spandam. - OG}Yeah, this is Spandam.{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, is this the chief? - OG}Oh! Is that you, Chief?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Good!\NI can finally give you a report! - OG}Finally! I have a report you need to hear!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I don't know where to start. - OG}Wh-Where do I start...?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Calm down, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You wanna talk about the Straw Hats, right? - OG}It's about the Straw Hats, isn't it?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:48.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What happened after the last\Nreport? Oh, wait! Listen. - OG}What happened since\Nthe last report? Oh! Better yet...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:54.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In your report, just briefly summarize\Nthe key points and speak loud and clear! - OG}just summarize the key points\Nand make it loud and clear!{TMM/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! The invaders–
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Did you accidentally kill them? - OG}You accidentally killed them?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, that's their own fault for being so weak–
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The pirates, who number about sixty, have invaded... - OG}{Approximately sixty pirates invaders... - Z}Approximately sixty pirate invaders...{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:10.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and pushed into the courthouse plaza,\Nthe farthest point on Enies Lobby's main island!  -OG}{have breached the courthouse plaza,\Nthe farthest point inland on Enies Lobby! - Z}{\q2}have breached the courthouse plaza,\Nthe innermost point on the main island!{Z/Evo/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:17.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To all units on Enies Lobby's main island! - OG}Calling all units on Enies Lobby's main island!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All soldiers!\NHead to the courthouse\Nplaza immediately! - OG}{All soldiers!\NReport to the courthouse plaza on the double! - Z}All soldiers! Head to\Nthe courthouse plaza at once!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You did a good job, Gomorrah! - OG}You really pulled through, Gomorrah!{ Z/Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:30.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We won't waste the effort you\Nand your brother made for us! - OG}{I promise you and your bro's efforts\Nwon't go to waste! - Z}I promise, you and your bro's\Nefforts won't go to waste!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're gonna attack, guys! - OG}Let's give 'em hell, boys!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We'll rescue Big Bro Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Yeah!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The pirates have reached the courthouse plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Can you see Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:06.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:17.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If the rooftop is that high,\Nwe can't just climb up there. - OG}The rooftop's a little high for us\Nto scale the side of the building.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:20.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No... It's not like we're made of rubber. - OG}Right. It's not like we're made of rubber.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How many CP9 members did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We only saw the big horn guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:33.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's hard to believe that all of them are in\Na place like that with Robin-chan and Franky. - OG}It's so surreal to think Robin and Franky\Nare up there with them in such a place.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:36.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In any case, we have to\Ncatch up with Luffy quickly! - OG}That aside, we have to hurry to Luffy!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've got to hurry and rescue Robin! -OG}Robin is running out of time!{Zenef: not a one-for-one translation, but it was redundant with Chopper's previous line.}{yup. The redundancy works in Japanese because it rhymes, but the syntax is inverted here. I like this. -arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hurry to the courthouse plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The drawbridge isn't down yet! Corner them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whoa! What an amazing frog! - OG}Whoa! That frog's awesome!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's the flail that knocked out Gomorrah!\NWhose is it?! - OG}{That's the flail that knocked out Gomorrah!\NWho threw that?! - Z}That's the flail that\Nknocked out Gomorrah! What a beast!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:16.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Over there! They're running away!\NThere are three of them! - OG}Over there! They're running away!\NI saw three of 'em!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are they running away? - OG}They're running now?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're the ones who started the attack. - OG}But they attacked first!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:25.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of time chasing after\Neach enemy who runs away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shut up. I just went to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:50.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It wouldn't hurt to know what kind of enemies would attack us, would it? - OG}It wouldn't hurt to know what kind of\Nenemies we're up against, would it?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:53.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Whoa! He brought him down!\N– Whoa! He brought him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:59.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He must have incredible strength\Nto swing around something like this! - OG}He's gotta be one helluva strong guy\Nto swing that thing around!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Does he belong to a special\Nunit like the Watchdogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There may be more hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, let's hurry up.\NThe guards are closing in on us. - OG}Let's scoot. The guards are closing in.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corner them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:17.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're not gonna be able to open\Nthe courthouse's heavy stone doors anyway! - OG}They'll never get those\Nheavy stone doors to budge!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finish them here in the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, these doors are huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How will we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,get them open...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll go on ahead! - OG}I'm going in!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,H-He cut through that thick stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:40.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zambai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:46.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll split up and go to both sides in order to pull down the drawbridge's levers! - OG}We gotta split up and head to either side\Nto pull both of the drawbridge levers!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:49.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{O-Okay! I'm counting on you guys! - OG}O-Okay! You got this!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right! We'll split into three groups! - OG}Okay! This means we split into three teams!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:57.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come with me to clean up the courthouse!\NI only need a few of you! - OG}We're gonna clean up the courthouse,\Nso a few of you will come with me!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Good luck, guys! Go! - OG}Good luck to the rest of you! Now go!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:13.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Also, the giant gatekeepers of the island gate , Oimo and\NKashi, went over to the pirates' side! - OG}Also, the giant gatekeepers, Oimo and Kashi,\Nwent over to the pirates' side!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:22.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They're currently around the center of the main\Nisland running towards the courthouse! - OG}{They're speeding down the island's\Nmain road toward the courthouse! - Z}They're speeding down the main road\Ntoward the courthouse!{Evo}{They're currently running back\Nup the main road! - arch: JP says "in the opposite direction [than expected]". Not exactly clear which direction, and the courthouse isn't mentioned at all. I'd interpret that they're clashing with the soldiers chasing the Straw Hats. If this is hard to understand, maybe just revert it to Evo/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get outta our way! - OG}Out of the way!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:33.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The casualties of our guards are... - OG}Guard casualties have reached...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}over 2,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Not five...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:44.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And the captain, Straw Hat Luffy,\Nwho beat over 1,000 all by himself, suddenly disappeared... - OG}{\q2}And the one who beat 1,000 all on his own,\NCaptain Straw Hat Luffy, suddenly disappeared...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{so we're searching for him right now! - OG}but we're searching for him as we speak!{Z/Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:55.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{[/i1] - This is probably unprecedented - the worst situation we've had in the history of Enies Lobby! - OG}{[/q2]This has to be unprecedented—\Nthe worst catastrophe Enies Lobby has ever faced! - arch: OG is a slight mistranslation, I believe. The "probably" is more of an "I dare say" - he wants to objectively communicate the severity of the situation to Spandam. "This is no doubt unprecedented" already sounds like a judgement to me, and it feels weird for him to talk to his superior that way}This has to be unprecedented—the worst\Ncatastrophe in the history of Enies Lobby!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Blueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's he doing in a place like that? - OG}What's he doing over there?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:09.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:16.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the hell is happening\Non this island right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:20.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Baskerville! Chief Justice Baskerville!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come in! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Whoa! Chief Spandam!\N– Whoa! Chief Spandam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is the left Baskerville on the left! - OG}On the left: the Left Baskerville!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is the right Baskerville on the right! - OG}On the right: the Right Baskerville!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,And in the center, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:34.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"All Alone Traveling the Central Main Line"! - so this is literal but as nonsensical as it is we could be very creative with this - arch}{\q2}"Alone and Unafraid Along the Central Main Line"!{Z- I hear you loud and clear. How about this using the common English idiom "alone and unafraid"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:35.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who the heck is that?! - OG}– Just who is that?!\N– Just who is that?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give me a status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:41.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I heard that the pirates have\Nalready made it to the courthouse plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Status?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm, status...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As for the status...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:53.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{More than the plaza,\Nthe inside of the courthouse is... - OG}The plaza aside,\Nthe inside of the courthouse...{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...in the most terrible state! - OG}– ...is in a terribly horrible state!\N– ...is in a terribly horrible state!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:07.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chief Justice! I have a report!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:13.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The pirates cut through the giant stone doors\Nand entered the courthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– I can see that already, you idiot!\N– I can see that already, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd see more enemies in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:22.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Looks like the way is clear,\Nbut what the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?! His head...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's like that guard dog from hell\NI heard about in some story! - OG}It's like the story of the guard dog from hell!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Berberus?!{Z- some kind of pun?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:32.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You mean Cerberus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Men! Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:37.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,This is a sacred chamber of law!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:42.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We will now cast judgment\Non your inevitable fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right, guys, - OG}All right, guys!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{head to the rooftop\Nwhere Straw Hat-san is! - OG}{Get to the rooftop\Nto be with Straw Hat! - Z}Get to the rooftop to join up with Straw Hat!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A group of us along with Yokozuna\Nwill stop pursuers at the doors. - OG}Yokozuna and the rest of us\Nwill hold off enemies at the doors!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:57.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've got your back,\Nso keep pushing forward! - OG}We've got your back,\Nso just keep pushing forward!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:01.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, look at that.\NLooks like the trial has started. - OG}Hey, look at that.\NThe trial just started.{Z- redundant "look" and "Looks"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.38,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Their crime is as follows!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:04.55,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}First, the act of stepping into Enies Lobby,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:07.18,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}which belongs to the World Government, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:04.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ignore it. It's just a bother!\NWhich way do we go?! - OG}Just ignore it! Which way do we go?!{arch: I'd just take it out, it's a one-word afterthought in JP, but every translation attempt makes it sound too purposeful}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Straight ahead! There are stairs on both sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll take them to the upper floors! - OG}Follow them to the top!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They ignored our sacred trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's unforgivable!\NHow dare they mock the Judicial Island?! - OG}{Unforgivable!\NThey dare mock the Judicial Island?! - Z}Unforgivable! They dare\Ndisrespect the Judicial Island?!{arch: Doesn't seem like a purposeful action on their part, they just don't give a shit. Could have used "make light of" if not for the CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:25.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on? His swords\Nlook like they're bending!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Charming Demon Sleepless Night...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Oni Giri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Is he the one who cut open the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:49.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The path is now open! - OG}The path's wide open!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:50.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:56.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So why is a guy who's that strong\Nnot their captain? - OG}How is a guy who's this\Nstrong not the captain?{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:02.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait! Wait! Wait! Outta my way!\NReindeer! Moron swordsman! - OG}Wait! Wait! Wait! Outta my way!\NReindeer! Swordsmoron!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Suit guy... - OG}{Suit Bro... - PP}Bro with the suit...{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a dangerous enemy camp! - OG}This is dangerous enemy territory!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:10.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll clear the path for Nami-san\Nto move forward! Outta my way! -OG}I'll clear the path so Nami can\Nmove forward! Outta my way!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?! Why is he starting a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You jerk! Are you picking a fight?! - OG}You want a piece of me, bastard?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:21.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up! You bastards are not\Nto get in Nami-san's way! -OG}Shut up! You cretins are\N{\i1}not{\i0} to get in Nami's way!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}, this way! Follow {\i1}only{\i0} me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, we came to rescue Robin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's right, Robin{-chan} is waiting\Nfor me to rescue her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Could she be crying right now\Nout of loneliness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:37.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We take our eyes off Zoro for a second, and now he's...! -OG}We look away for one second, and Zoro's...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:45.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wait, Zoro! That's the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:51.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{I said the stairs!\NJust what made you think you should go that way?! What fantasy world are you in?! -OG}I said the {\i1}stairs{\i0}! Why the hell would you think\Nto go that way?! What fantasy world are you in?!{Evo: marking another instance of hell for later just in case.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It was because\Nyou didn't explain it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no way it was my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro, I'll try making some medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{something that cures the oblivious. - OG}to cure idiocy.{Evo: I feel it's better to just be direct and simple here. I also considered "senselessness" or "lack of sense" as it could be taken as a jab at "sense of direction" as well, but decided to go full-on simple for now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oblivious...? - OG}Idio– Hey!{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:03.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hmm? - OG}Yeah?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:07.38,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]Robin-[/i1]chwan[/i0]! I'm coming now! - OG}{\an8}Robin my love! I'm coming now!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Make sure it works on that guy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Er... Yeah, okay, got it. - OG}Um... Okay, will do.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if Big Bro will be rescued safely. - OG}I wonder if Big Bro will come out of this alive.{arch: Don't like the passive voice in the OG line, but this can be reverted if necessary.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:15.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're the type that gets it together\Nwhen the going gets tough... - OG}When the going gets tough,\Nthey're the ones that get the job done...{Z/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:19.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,probably... I'm sure... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a big crime. - OG}This is a grave crime.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is a huge crime! - OG}A crime of the highest magnitude!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:27.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then, we'll pick the one in the middle: - OG}Then, we'll compromise and choose...{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:28.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Agreed!\N– Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:35.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– I'm the chief justice. Don't ignore me!\N– I'm the chief justice. Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper. Nami. Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll follow you after I take care of this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You think you can defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What a cocky pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how terrifying I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:05.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Heave-ho! Heave-ho!\N– Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll take you on, Cerberus! - OG}{\i1}We'll{\i0} take you on, Cerberus!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:31.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Ah... yeah.\N– Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,My face door finally closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of course. - OG}Naturally.{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,An opened door\Nis meant to close.{OG/arch}{It wouldn't be a door if it didn't close. - Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:59.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm surprised that you could\Ndodge my Tempest Kick. - OG}I am surprised you could\Ndodge my tempest kick.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Well, it's a piece of cake. - OG}Yeah... because it's not that hard.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I resent that. - OG}That's regrettable.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:14.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:16.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Iron Body: Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:24.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Iron Body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:31.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.46,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's keeping up with me. - OG}He is perfectly keeping up with me.{PP/arch: He is keeping up with all of my attacks. - arch: alternative, but slightly less accurate and doesn't fit the next line. Lit: "He is completely matching my speed"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.75,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,He altered my tempest kick's course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.67,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's got unbelievable physical abilities! - OG}He has unbelievable physical abilities!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:54.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,This won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:59.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm no good like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:04.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,When I lost to Aokiji, I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:08.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{"If run into guys this powerful on the sea ahead, -OG}"If I run into guys this powerful\Non the sea ahead,{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't be able to protect my friends unless I get much stronger. - OG}{unless I get much stronger,\NI won't be able to protect my friends." - Z}I won't be able to protect my friends...{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:13.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't be able to protect my friends unless I get much stronger. - OG}{unless I get much stronger,\NI won't be able to protect my friends." - Z}unless I get much stronger."{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:20.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I want my friends by my side\Neven if some of them are not at that level. - OG}I want my friends by my side,\Neven if they're not all as strong as me.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I've got to be stronger...{Lit. it's "I've got to be the strongest" or "I've got to be stronger than anyone else", but I don't see a good way to translate that. - arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:26.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,or I'll lose them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then... what're you gonna do? - OG}Then... what will you do?{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I came up with a way\Nto fight with all my might...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,so that I won't lose anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,so that no one will be taken away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.76,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's he doing? - OG}What is he doing?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.27,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's happening inside his body?! - OG}What is happening inside his body?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:50.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, you... - OG}And now...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{are no match for me. -OG}you won't be able to keep up anymore.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:59.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All my other abilities are now on another level. - OG}{All my abilities are now on another level. - Evo: I'm hesitant about the repetition of "now" but I don't know if there's a way of preventing this without making anything sound odd.}{My techniques will evolve to a whole new level. - arch: He might be specifically talking about his moves/attacks here, which will all get "Jet" versions.}My techniques will all evolve to a new level.{arch: More literal but sounds way worse, not worth it imo}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:03.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gear Second!
